.jpg|50px]] \n| '''''Condors'''''\n|-\n| '''[[Marine Wing Support Squadron 274]]''' \n| [[File:MWSS-274 Squadron Insignia.png|50px]]\n| '''''Ironmen'''''\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n==== [[Marine Aircraft Group 31]] ====\n[[File:MAG31beaufort.jpg|left|150px]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|- \n! Squadron Name !! Insignia !! Nickname\n|-\n| '''[[Marine Aviation Logistics Squadron 31]]''' \n| [[File:Mals-31.jpg|50px]] \n| '''''Stingers'''''\n|-\n| '''[[VMFA-115|Marine Fighter Attack Squadron 115]]''' \n| [[File:VMFA-115 insignia.jpg|50px]] \n| '''''Silver Eagles'''''\n|-\n| '''[[VMFA(AW)-224|Marine All Weather Fighter Attack Squadron 224]]''' \n| [[File:VMFA-224.png|50px]] \n| '''''Bengals'''''\n|-\n| '''[[VMFA-251|Marine Fighter Attack Squadron 251]]''' \n| [[File:VMFA-251.png|50px]] \n| '''''Thunderbolts'''''\n|-\n| '''[[VMFA-312|Marine Fighter Attack Squadron 312]]''' \n| [[File:VMFA-312.png|50px]] \n| '''''Checkerboards'''''\n|-\n| '''[[VMFAT-501|Marine Fighter Attack Training Squadron 501]]''' \n| [[File:VMFAT-501.png|50px]] \n| '''''Warlords'''''\n|-\n| '''[[VMFA(AW)-533|Marine All Weather Fighter Attack Squadron 533]]''' \n| [[File:VMFA-533.png|50px]] \n| '''''Hawks'''''\n|-\n| '''[[Marine Wing Support Squadron 273]]''' \n| [[File:Mwss273 insig.jpg|50px]] \n| '''''Sweathogs'''''\n|}\n{{clear}}\n\n==== [[Marine Air Control Group 28]] ====\n[[File:MACG-28 insignia.gif|left|150px]]\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|- \n! Squadron Name !! Insignia !! Nickname\n|-\n| '''[[Marine Tactical Air Command Squadron 28]]''' \n| [[File:MTATCS-28 insignia.GIF|60px]] \n|\n|-\n| '''[[Marine Air Control Squadron 2]]''' \n| [[File:Marine Air Control Squadron High Quality Insignia.png|50px]] \n| '''''Eyes of the MAGTF'''''\n|-\n| '''[[Marine Air Support Squadron 1]]''' \n| [[File:MASS-1 squadron insignia.png|50px]] \n| ''''' Atlantic Nomads'''''\n|-\n| '''[[Marine Wing Communications Squadron 28]]''' \n| [[File:MWCS28.jpg|50px